00:58:05,393 --> 00:58:06,235
Rym: You come into the game.

732
00:58:06,857 --> 00:58:11,650
Rym: There are no Metro until the very, very, very end of the game.

733
00:58:12,591 --> 00:58:14,702
Scott: Well, I think that Nintendo had a pattern of that, right?

734
00:58:14,722 --> 00:58:16,169
Scott: Zelda was legend of Zelda.

735
00:58:16,189 --> 00:58:18,359
Scott: It was, it was not named after the name character.

736
00:58:18,580 --> 00:58:18,921
Scott: It's like.

737
00:58:19,203 --> 00:58:20,147
Scott: Metroid is not named.

738
00:58:20,167 --> 00:58:21,735
Scott: The main character is Sam is not right.

739
00:58:21,795 --> 00:58:23,161
Scott: It's like, you know, Mario.

740
00:58:23,181 --> 00:58:25,995
Scott: It's like, okay, the name of the game is the name of the main character.

741
00:58:26,095 --> 00:58:28,747
Scott: You know, Sonic, the name of the game is the main character.

742
00:58:28,848 --> 00:58:29,692
Scott: Zelda and Metroid.

743
00:58:29,732 --> 00:58:30,315
Scott: No, it's not.

