00:58:32,546 --> 00:58:34,576
Scott: It's the name of something else, right?

746
00:58:35,159 --> 00:58:37,991
Rym: But then you finally encounter Metroids and they're just all up in your grill.

747
00:58:38,011 --> 00:58:40,359
Rym: There's a million of them constantly coming at you and it's crazy.

748
00:58:41,503 --> 00:58:41,664
Scott: Yep.

749
00:58:42,185 --> 00:58:52,380
Rym: So the thing they get the mechanic, cause every Metroid game, well, most measure games have like either a new mechanic or the thing that's interesting about this Metroid.

